      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently maintained. Mechanically, it is very reliable; the engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts precisely, and all major systems are functioning as they should. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of normal use, such as small stone chips and light wear on the driver's seat, the car remains clean and presentable. It is a dependable choice for anyone seeking a well-cared-for vehicle that is ready for the road.",
