    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for those prioritizing utility over appearance. The exterior shows typical signs of age, including noticeable paint fading on the roof and hood, along with various small scuffs and door dings. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few minor stains, but remains intact and functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it may soon require routine maintenance for wear-and-tear items like brake pads or tires. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that has plenty of life left for a daily commuter.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
