      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to acquire a showroom-ready masterpiece. This vehicle stands in impeccable condition, having been curated with an uncompromising commitment to maintenance and care. Every surface, from the flawless paintwork to the pristine interior, reflects its status as a premier example of the model. Engineered for those who demand excellence, this car offers a driving experience indistinguishable from new. We invite discerning enthusiasts to witness this benchmark of quality firsthand.",
