    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Stepping into this car is like stepping back into a moment of pure, unadulterated perfection. The exterior boasts a finish so deep and lustrous it feels like looking into a still mountain lake, while the interior is a sanctuary of pristine leather and gleaming accents that have been untouched by the passage of time. This is more than a machine; it is a symphony of engineering and grace, offering a whisper-quiet cabin and a ride that feels like gliding on silk. It has been curated with the kind of soul-deep devotion usually reserved for fine art, preserved in a state that defies the calendar. To drive it is to command a legacy of elegance that turns every mundane errand into a grand tour.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
